Note: Only auto attacks can critically strike, but Greedent has 0% base Critical-Hit rate at all levels.

Skwovet

Evolves At 5

Cheek Pouch

Passive Ability

When Greedent eats a berry, recover HP after receiving the effects of the berry (oran berry or unite move berry 1%Max HP + 3x(Lv-1) + 23; sitrus or salac berry 1%Max HP + 0x(Lv-1) + 23). At the same time, Greedent stashes an Oran berry in its tail. Being hit by a single attack or combination of attacks will cause an Oran berry to drop from Greedent's tail (4.5s cd). Berries stay on the ground for 10s.

All players heal from an oran berry for 2% Max HP + 5x(Level-1) + 45, level and Max HP scaling is based on the player that ate the oran berry.

Attack

Auto Attack

Becomes a boosted attack with every third attack, dealing increased damage when it hits and causing one Oran berry to drop from Greedent's tail.

100% Atk + 0 x (Level - 1) + 0

75% Atk + 4 x (Level - 1) + 80

Tackle

Move 1

5.50s Dash

Leap to the designated area, dealing damage to enemies in the area of effect and decreasing their movement speed by 20% for 1s. If this move is used while Covet is active, no area can be designated for Greedent to leap to. Instead, while running, damage is dealt in an area to enemies in front of Greedent. If Greedent has any Oran berries stashed, consume all of them, reducing Tackle's cooldown by 1s for each berry consumed.

101% Atk + 16 x (Level - 1) + 310

Tackle Upgrade Choices

Bullet Seed

4.50s Ranged

Spit berry seeds in the designated direction for 6s; dealing damage to enemies in the area of effect and decreasing their movement speed by 30% for 1s. Greedent fires more seeds for each Oran berry stashed.

33% Atk + 4 x (Level - 1) + 80

Increased damage.

35% Atk + 4 x (Level - 1) + 90

Belch

5.00s Ranged

Deals damage to enemies in the area of effect and decrease their movement speed by 40% for 2s, decreasing by 10% every 0.5s. If Greedent has any Oran berries stashed, consume all of them, reducing Belch's cooldown by 1s for each berry consumed (capping at 4s). This move's cooldown cannot be reduced beyond 1s.

194.7% Atk + 34 x (Level - 1) + 736

Increased damage.

207% Atk + 36 x (Level - 1) + 788

Defense Curl

Move 2

8.00s Buff

Grants Greedent a shield (10% max HP) for 3s. In addition, an Oran berry will drop in front of Greedent.

Defense Curl Upgrade Choices

Stuff Cheeks

8.00s Buff

Greedent drops 5 Oran berries, which can be eaten to recover HP. Any HP recovered from an Oran berry eaten within 5s that exceeds Greedent's max HP will be converted to a shield for 1.8% max HP per berry (capped at 9% max HP or 5 berries). If Greedent catches sight of a berry while using this move, movement speed is increased by 70% for 6s, but decreasing by 15% every 1s.

Increase the number of Oran berries dropped by 1.

Covet

10.00s Hindrance

Greedent runs with all its might for 6s; becoming resistant to hindrances (for 6.1s), dealing damage to enemies hit and throwing them. While running; Greedent drops Oran berries every 1s. Eating a dropped berry increases movement speed by 22% for 1s (stacking up to 5 times). In addition, Tackle, Belch or Bullet Seed can also be used while running and using this move will reset the cooldown of Tackle or Belch.

55% Atk + 4 x (Level - 1) + 180

Increased damage and increased frequency of Oran berries dropping (8 berries over 6s).

59% Atk + 5 x (Level - 1) + 200

Berry Belly Flop

Unite Move

100s 90000 Area

Unlocks at level 9

Greedent eats a special berry to recover 15% max HP and then leaps to the designated area; dealing damage and throwing enemies within the area of effect. Greedent then eats another berry, allowing an unlimited amount of Oran berries to be stored for 8s and resets cooldowns of all moves. Greedent is unstoppable during this move.

241% Atk + 22 x (Level - 1) + 1050

Unite Buffs (6s duration):

30% Movement Speed, 40% Max HP Shield
